## Priority Table Updates

Always update the priority table in `docs/10X_IMPROVEMENTS.md` when:
- Starting work on an item (change Status to "In Progress")
- Completing an item (change Status to "Done", mark with ‚úÖ)
- Cancelling an item (change Status to "Cancelled")

## Verification Checklist

Before marking a task complete:

- [ ] Code implemented
- [ ] Tests added/updated
- [ ] Documentation updated (per documentation.mdc)
- [ ] Status updated in 10X_IMPROVEMENTS.md
- [ ] Priority table updated
- [ ] Examples added if user-facing
- [ ] Breaking changes documented if any

